trans-unit.source: Retrieves a resource.
trans-unit.target: 检索资源。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a resource. This resource can be of the following three return types: (1) java.io.InputStream (2) javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamReader (3) java.xml.stream.XMLEventReader. If this method returns null the processor will attempt to resolve the entity using its default mechanism.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个资源。这个资源可以是以下三种返回类型。(1)java.io.InputStream (2)javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamReader (3)java.xml.stream.XMLEventReader。如果该方法返回null,处理器将尝试使用其默认机制解析实体。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set holding the elements of the subarray that starts at Retrieves a ResultSet object that contains a subarray of the elements in this SerialArray object, starting at index
trans-unit.target: 检索一个包含从此处开始的子数组元素的结果集。检索一个 ResultSet 对象，该对象包含此 SerialArray 对象中元素的子数组，从index开始。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set holding the elements of the subarray that starts at index index and contains up to count successive elements.
trans-unit.target: 获取结果集保持，在开始索引的子阵列中的元素 index 并且包含多达 count 个连续元素。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set holding the elements of the subarray that starts at index index and contains up to count successive elements. This method uses the connection's type map to map the elements of the array if the map contains an entry for the base type. Otherwise, the standard mapping is used.
trans-unit.target: 获取结果集保持，在开始索引的子阵列中的元素 index 并且包含多达 count 个连续元素。如果该映射包含基本类型的条目，则此方法使用连接的类型映射来映射数组的元素。否则，将使用标准映射。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set holding the elements of the subarray that starts at index index and contains up to count successive elements. This method uses the specified map for type map customizations unless the base type of the array does not match a user-defined type in map, in which case it uses the standard mapping. This version of the method getResultSet uses either the given type map or the standard mapping; it never uses the type map associated with the connection.
trans-unit.target: 获取结果集保持，在开始索引的子阵列中的元素 index 并且包含多达 count 个连续元素。此方法使用指定的 map 为类型映射自定义，除非该数组的基本类型不匹配的用户定义类型 map ，在这种情况下，它使用标准映射。此版本的 getResultSet 方法使用给定的类型映射或标准映射。它从不使用与连接关联的类型映射。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set that contains the elements of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object.
trans-unit.target: 检索结果集，该结果集包含此 Array 对象指定的SQL ARRAY 值的元素。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set that contains the elements of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object. If appropriate, the elements of the array are mapped using the connection's type map; otherwise, the standard mapping is used.
trans-unit.target: 检索结果集，该结果集包含此 Array 对象指定的SQL ARRAY 值的元素。如果合适的话，使用连接的类型映射来映射数组的元素；否则，将使用标准映射。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a result set that contains the elements of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object. This method uses the specified map for type map customizations unless the base type of the array does not match a user-defined type in map, in which case it uses the standard mapping. This version of the method getResultSet uses either the given type map or the standard mapping; it never uses the type map associated with the connection.
trans-unit.target: 检索结果集，该结果集包含此 Array 对象指定的SQL ARRAY 值的元素。此方法使用指定的 map 为类型映射自定义，除非该数组的基本类型不匹配的用户定义类型 map ，在这种情况下，它使用标准映射。此版本的 getResultSet 方法使用给定的类型映射或标准映射。它从不使用与连接关联的类型映射。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a server socket associated with this channel.
trans-unit.target: 检索与该通道相关联的服务器套接字。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a slice of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object, beginning with the specified index and containing up to count successive elements of the SQL array.
trans-unit.target: 检索SQL的切片 ARRAY 由该指定值 Array 对象，从指定开始 index 和含有最多 count SQL数组中连续元素。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a slice of the SQL ARRAY value designated by this Array object, beginning with the specified index and containing up to count successive elements of the SQL array. This method uses the type map associated with the connection for customizations of the type mappings.
trans-unit.target: 检索SQL的切片 ARRAY 由该指定值 Array 对象，从指定开始 index 和含有最多 count SQL数组中连续元素。此方法使用与连接关联的类型映射来自定义类型映射。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a socket associated with this channel.
trans-unit.target: 检索与该通道相关联的套接字。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream that can be used to write the XML value that this SQLXML instance represents.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个流,可以用来写这个SQLXML实例所代表的XML值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream that can be used to write the XML value that this SQLXML instance represents. The stream begins at position 0. The bytes of the stream are interpreted according to appendix F of the XML 1.0 specification The behavior of this method is the same as ResultSet.updateBinaryStream() when the designated column of the ResultSet has a type java.sql.Types of SQLXML.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个流,这个流可以用来写入这个SQLXML实例所代表的XML值。当ResultSet的指定列的类型为java.sql.Types of SQLXML时,该方法的行为与ResultSet.updateBinaryStream()相同。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream that can be used to write to the BLOB value that this Blob object represents.
trans-unit.target: 检索可用于写入此 Blob 对象表示的 BLOB 值的流。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream that can be used to write to the BLOB value that this Blob object represents. The stream begins at position pos. The bytes written to the stream will overwrite the existing bytes in the Blob object starting at the position pos. If the end of the Blob value is reached while writing to the stream, then the length of the Blob value will be increased to accommodate the extra bytes.
trans-unit.target: 检索可用于写入此 Blob 对象表示的 BLOB 值的流。流从位置 pos 开始。从位置 pos 开始，写入流的字节将覆盖 Blob 对象中的现有字节。如果的端部 Blob 当写入到流达到的值，则长度 Blob 值将增加以容纳额外的字节。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream that can be used to write to the BLOB value that this Blob object represents. The stream begins at position pos. This method forwards the setBinaryStream() call to the underlying Blob in the event that this SerialBlob object is instantiated with a Blob. If this SerialBlob is instantiated with a byte array, a SerialException is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 检索可用于写入此 Blob 对象表示的 BLOB 值的流。流从位置 pos 开始。转发该方法中 setBinaryStream() 调用底层 Blob 在事件，这 SerialBlob 对象被实例化与 Blob 。如果使用 byte 数组实例化此 SerialBlob ，则抛出 SerialException 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write Ascii characters to the CLOB value that this Clob object represents, starting at position pos.
trans-unit.target: 从位置 pos 检索用于将Ascii字符写入此 Clob 对象表示的 CLOB 值的流。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write Ascii characters to the CLOB value that this Clob object represents, starting at position pos. Characters written to the stream will overwrite the existing characters in the Clob object starting at the position pos. If the end of the Clob value is reached while writing characters to the stream, then the length of the Clob value will be increased to accommodate the extra characters.
trans-unit.target: 从位置 pos 检索用于将Ascii字符写入此 Clob 对象表示的 CLOB 值的流。从位置 pos 开始，写入流中的字符将覆盖 Clob 对象中的现有字符。如果的端部 Clob 而写入字符到流达到的值，则长度 Clob 值将增加以容纳额外的字符。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write Ascii characters to the CLOB value that this SerialClob object represents, starting at position pos.
trans-unit.target: 从位置 pos 检索用于将Ascii字符写入此 SerialClob 对象表示的 CLOB 值的流。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write Ascii characters to the CLOB value that this SerialClob object represents, starting at position pos. This method forwards the setAsciiStream() call to the underlying Clob object in the event that this SerialClob object is instantiated with a Clob object. If this SerialClob object is instantiated with a char array, a SerialException object is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 从位置 pos 检索用于将Ascii字符写入此 SerialClob 对象表示的 CLOB 值的流。转发该方法的 setAsciiStream() 调用底层 Clob 对象在事件，这 SerialClob 对象被实例化用 Clob 对象。如果使用 char 数组实例化此 SerialClob 对象，则将引发 SerialException 对象。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write a stream of Unicode characters to the CLOB value that this Clob object represents, at position pos.
trans-unit.target: 检索用于将Unicode字符流写入此 Clob 对象表示的 CLOB 值（位置 pos )的流。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write a stream of Unicode characters to the CLOB value that this Clob object represents, at position pos. Characters written to the stream will overwrite the existing characters in the Clob object starting at the position pos. If the end of the Clob value is reached while writing characters to the stream, then the length of the Clob value will be increased to accommodate the extra characters.
trans-unit.target: 检索用于将Unicode字符流写入此 Clob 对象表示的 CLOB 值（位置 pos )的流。从位置 pos 开始，写入流中的字符将覆盖 Clob 对象中的现有字符。如果的端部 Clob 而写入字符到流达到的值，则长度 Clob 值将增加以容纳额外的字符。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write a stream of Unicode characters to the CLOB value that this SerialClob object represents, at position pos.
trans-unit.target: 检索用于将Unicode字符流写入此 SerialClob 对象表示的 CLOB 值（位置 pos )的流。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write a stream of Unicode characters to the CLOB value that this SerialClob object represents, at position pos. This method forwards the setCharacterStream() call to the underlying Clob object in the event that this SerialClob object is instantiated with a Clob object. If this SerialClob object is instantiated with a char array, a SerialException is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 检索用于将Unicode字符流写入此 SerialClob 对象表示的 CLOB 值（位置 pos )的流。转发该方法中 setCharacterStream() 调用底层 Clob 对象在事件，这 SerialClob 对象被实例化用 Clob 对象。如果使用 char 数组实例化此 SerialClob 对象，则会引发 SerialException 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write the XML value that this SQLXML instance represents.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个流,用来写入这个SQLXML实例所代表的XML值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a stream to be used to write the XML value that this SQLXML instance represents. The format of this stream is defined by org.xml.sax.InputSource, where the characters in the stream represent the unicode code points for XML according to section 2 and appendix B of the XML 1.0 specification. Although an encoding declaration other than unicode may be present, the encoding of the stream is unicode. The behavior of this method is the same as ResultSet.updateCharacterStream() when the designated column of the ResultSet has a type java.sql.Types of SQLXML.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个流,用于写入这个SQLXML实例所代表的XML值。这个流的格式由org.xml.sax.InputSource定义,其中流中的字符代表了根据XML 1.0规范第2节和附录B的XML的unicode码点。虽然可能存在除unicode以外的编码声明,但流的编码是unicode。当ResultSet的指定列具有类型为java.sql.Types的SQLXML时,该方法的行为与ResultSet.updateCharacterStream()相同。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a string explaining the minor status code.
trans-unit.target: 检索解释小状态代码的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a value set in the state of this engine.
trans-unit.target: 检索本引擎状态下设置的值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a value set in the state of this engine. The value might be one which was set using setValue or some other value in the state of the ScriptEngine, depending on the implementation. Must have the same effect as getBindings(ScriptContext.ENGINE_SCOPE).get
trans-unit.target: 检索在此引擎状态下设置的值。该值可以是使用 setValue 设置的值，也可以是 ScriptEngine 状态下的其他某个值，具体取决于实现方式。必须具有与 getBindings(ScriptContext.ENGINE_SCOPE).get 相同的效果

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all TIFF fields from the directory.
trans-unit.target: 检索目录中的所有TIFF字段。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all of the attributes associated with a named object.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象相关联的所有属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all of the attributes associated with a named object. See getAttributes(Name) for details.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象关联的所有属性。有关详细信息，请参见 getAttributes(Name) 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all of the attributes associated with a named object. See DirContext.getAttributes(Name) for details.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象关联的所有属性。有关详细信息，请参见 DirContext.getAttributes(Name) 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all of the attributes associated with a named object. See getAttributes(Name) for details.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象关联的所有属性。有关详细信息，请参见 getAttributes(Name) 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all of the attributes associated with a named object. See the class description regarding attribute models, attribute type names, and operational attributes.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象相关联的所有属性。关于属性模型、属性类型名称和操作属性,请参见类的描述。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all or part of the BLOB value that this Blob object represents, as an array of bytes.
trans-unit.target: 以字节数组形式检索此 Blob 对象表示的全部或部分 BLOB 值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all or part of the BLOB value that this Blob object represents, as an array of bytes. This byte array contains up to length consecutive bytes starting at position pos.
trans-unit.target: 以字节数组形式检索此 Blob 对象表示的全部或部分 BLOB 值。该 byte 数组包含从位置 pos 开始的 length 连续字节。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves all the "extra" characters that can be used in unquoted identifier names (those beyond a-z, A-Z, 0-9 and _).
trans-unit.target: 检索所有可以用于未引号标识符名称的 "额外 "字符(a-z、A-Z、0-9和_以外的字符)。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an Attr node by local name and namespace URI.
trans-unit.target: 通过本地名称和名称空间URI检索 Attr 节点。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an XAResource object that the transaction manager will use to manage this XAConnection object's participation in a distributed transaction.
trans-unit.target: 检索 XAResource 对象，事务管理器将使用该XAResource对象来管理此 XAConnection 对象对分布式事务的参与。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an Enumeration with all of the currently loaded JDBC drivers to which the current caller has access.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个包含当前调用者可以访问的所有当前加载的JDBC驱动程序的枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an RDN of this LDAP name as an Rdn.
trans-unit.target: 检索此LDAP名称的RDN作为Rdn。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an array containing the parameter values (both Objects and primitives) that have been set for this RowSet object's command and throws an SQLException object if all parameters have not been set.
trans-unit.target: 检索包含为此 RowSet 对象的命令设置的参数值（对象和基元）的数组，如果尚未设置所有参数，则抛出 SQLException 对象。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an array containing the parameter values (both Objects and primitives) that have been set for this RowSet object's command and throws an SQLException object if all parameters have not been set. Before the command is sent to the DBMS to be executed, these parameters will be substituted for placeholder parameters in the PreparedStatement object that is the command for a RowSet implementation extending the BaseRowSet class.
trans-unit.target: 检索包含为此 RowSet 对象的命令设置的参数值（对象和基元）的数组，如果尚未设置所有参数，则抛出 SQLException 对象。在将命令发送到DBMS执行之前，这些参数将替换 PreparedStatement 对象中的占位符参数，该对象是扩展 BaseRowSet 类的 RowSet 实现的命令。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an array of Controls from the object that implements this interface.
trans-unit.target: 从实现此接口的对象中检索 Control 的数组。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an array of Controls from the object that implements this interface. It is null if there are no controls.
trans-unit.target: 从实现此接口的对象中检索 Control 的数组。如果没有控件，则为null。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an array of Object values containing the attributes of the SQL structured type that this SerialStruct object represents.
trans-unit.target: 检索包含此 SerialStruct 对象表示的SQL结构化类型的属性的 Object 值的数组。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an attribute node by name.
trans-unit.target: 按名称检索属性节点。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an attribute value by local name and namespace URI.
trans-unit.target: 通过本地名称和命名空间URI检索属性值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an attribute value by name.
trans-unit.target: 按名称检索属性值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the addresses in this reference.
trans-unit.target: 检索此引用中的地址枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the addresses in this reference. When addresses are added, changed or removed from this reference, its effects on this enumeration are undefined.
trans-unit.target: 检索此引用中地址的枚举。当地址被添加、更改或删除时,其对该枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the attribute's values.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性值的枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the attribute's values. The behaviour of this enumeration is unspecified if the attribute's values are added, changed, or removed while the enumeration is in progress. If the attribute values are ordered, the enumeration's items will be ordered.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性值的枚举。如果属性值在枚举过程中被添加、更改或删除,则该枚举的行为未被指定。如果属性值是有序的,则枚举的项将是有序的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the attributes in the attribute set.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性集中的属性枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the attributes in the attribute set. The effects of updates to this attribute set on this enumeration are undefined.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性集中属性的枚举。对该属性集的更新对该枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the ids of the attributes in the attribute set.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性集中属性ID的枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of the ids of the attributes in the attribute set. The effects of updates to this attribute set on this enumeration are undefined.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性集中属性ID的枚举。此属性集的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumeration of this attribute's values.
trans-unit.target: 检索此属性值的枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an indexed member of a JavaScript object.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个JavaScript对象的索引成员。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an indexed member of a JavaScript object. Equivalent to "this[index]" in JavaScript.
trans-unit.target: 检索一个JavaScript对象的索引成员,相当于JavaScript中的 "this[index]"。相当于JavaScript中的 "this[index]"。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an unmodifiable lexicographically increasing set of tag names.
trans-unit.target: 检索不可修改的递增的标签名集。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an unmodifiable numerically increasing set of tag numbers.
trans-unit.target: 检索一组不可修改的递增数字标签号。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes all pending events for this watch key, returning a List of the events that were retrieved.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此监视键的所有未决事件，并返回已检索事件的 List 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes next watch key, waiting if none are yet present.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除下一个手表钥匙,如果没有,则等待。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the Future representing the next completed task, or null if none are present.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除表示下一个已完成任务的Future，如果不存在则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the Future representing the next completed task, waiting if necessary up to the specified wait time if none are yet present.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除代表下一个已完成任务的 "未来",如果还没有任务,则在指定的等待时间内等待。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the Future representing the next completed task, waiting if none are yet present.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除代表下一个已完成任务的 "未来",如果还没有,则等待。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first (lowest) element, or returns null if this set is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除第一个（最低）元素，如果此集合为空，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque, or returns null if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列的第一个元素，如果此双端队列为空，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque, waiting if necessary until an element becomes available.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该deque的第一个元素,必要时等待,直到有元素可用。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque, waiting up to the specified wait time if necessary for an element to become available.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该deque中的第一个元素,如果需要等待一个元素可用,则需要等待指定的时间。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该deque的第一个元素。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque. This method differs from pollFirst only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列的第一个元素。此方法与 pollFirst 的不同之处仅在于，如果此双端队列为空，则它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque. This method differs from pollFirst only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列的第一个元素。此方法与 pollFirst 的不同之处仅在于，如果此双端队列为空，则它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque. This method differs from pollFirst only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the first element of this deque. This method differs from pollFirst only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties and no controls. The referral context is created using env as its environment properties and no controls.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties.
trans-unit.target: 检索使用环境属性继续方法的上下文。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索使用环境属性继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是间接遇到的,例如在搜索枚举中,引用异常都应该提供一个继续操作的上下文。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using request controls and environment properties. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation. To continue the operation, the client program should re-invoke the method using the same arguments as the original invocation.
trans-unit.target: 使用请求控件和环境属性检索继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是在搜索枚举中间接遇到的,引用异常都应该提供一个可以继续操作的上下文。为了继续操作,客户端程序应该使用与原始调用相同的参数重新调用该方法。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using the context's environment and no controls.
trans-unit.target: 检索上下文,在此上下文中使用上下文的环境而不使用控制来继续该方法。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using the context's environment and no controls. The referral context is created using the environment properties of the context that threw the ReferralException and no controls.
trans-unit.target: 检索上下文，使用上下文环境在没有控件的情况下继续该方法。引用上下文是使用抛出 ReferralException 且没有控件的上下文的环境属性创建的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method. The referral context is created using the environment properties of the context that threw the ReferralException.
trans-unit.target: 检索继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是在搜索枚举中间接遇到的,引用异常都应该提供一个继续操作的上下文。引用上下文是使用抛出 ReferralException 的上下文的环境属性创建的。

trans-unit.target: 检索指定参数的指定列大小。

trans-unit.target: 检索此上下文的有效环境。关于环境属性的更多细节请参见类描述。

trans-unit.target: 检索此 ResultSet 对象的获取方向。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the first warning reported by calls on this Connection object.
trans-unit.target: 检索此 Connection 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the first warning reported by calls on this Connection object. If there is more than one warning, subsequent warnings will be chained to the first one and can be retrieved by calling the method SQLWarning.getNextWarning on the warning that was retrieved previously.
trans-unit.target: 检索此 Connection 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。如果存在多个警告，则随后的警告将链接到第一个警告，并且可以通过对先前检索到的警告调用方法 SQLWarning.getNextWarning 来检索。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the first warning reported by calls on this JdbcRowSet object.
trans-unit.target: 检索此 JdbcRowSet 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the first warning reported by calls on this JdbcRowSet object. If a second warning was reported on this JdbcRowSet object, it will be chained to the first warning and can be retrieved by calling the method RowSetWarning.getNextWarning on the first warning. Subsequent warnings on this JdbcRowSet object will be chained to the RowSetWarning objects returned by the method RowSetWarning.getNextWarning. The warning chain is automatically cleared each time a new row is read. This method may not be called on a RowSet object that has been closed; doing so will cause an SQLException to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 检索此 JdbcRowSet 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。如果在此 JdbcRowSet 对象上报告了第二条警告，它将被链接到第一个警告，并且可以通过在第一个警告上调用方法 RowSetWarning.getNextWarning 来进行检索。关于此 JdbcRowSet 对象的后续警告将链接到方法 RowSetWarning.getNextWarning 返回的 RowSetWarning 对象。每次读取新行时，警告链都会自动清除。不能在已关闭的 RowSet 对象上调用此方法。这样做将导致引发 SQLException 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the first warning reported by calls on this ResultSet object.

trans-unit.target: 检索此 ResultSet 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。此 ResultSet 对象上的后续警告将链接到此方法返回的 SQLWarning 对象。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the first warning reported by calls on this RowSet object.

The warning chain is automatically cleared each time a new row is read. This method may not be called on a RowSet object that has been closed; doing so will cause a SQLException to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 检索此 RowSet 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。此 RowSet 对象上的后续警告将链接到此方法返回的 RowSetWarning 对象。每次读取新行时，警告链都会自动清除。不能在已关闭的RowSet对象上调用此方法。这样做将导致引发 SQLException 。

trans-unit.target: 检索此 Statement 对象上的调用报告的第一个警告。后续的 Statement 对象警告将链接到此 SQLWarning 对象。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the flag bits describing the conversion properties of this transform.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the flag bits describing the conversion properties of this transform. The return value is either one of the constants TYPE_IDENTITY or TYPE_GENERAL_TRANSFORM, or a combination of the appropriate flag bits. A valid combination of flag bits is an exclusive OR operation that can combine the TYPE_TRANSLATION flag bit in addition to either of the TYPE_UNIFORM_SCALE or TYPE_GENERAL_SCALE flag bits as well as either of the TYPE_QUADRANT_ROTATION or TYPE_GENERAL_ROTATION flag bits.
trans-unit.target: 读取描述此变换的转换属性的标志位,返回值是常量TYPE_IDENTITY或TYPE_GENERAL_TRANSFORM中的一个。返回值是常量TYPE_IDENTITY或TYPE_GENERAL_TRANSFORM中的一个,或者是相应标志位的组合。有效的标志位组合是一个排他性的OR操作,除了TYPE_TRANSLATION标志位外,还可以结合TYPE_UNIFORM_SCALE或TYPE_GENERAL_SCALE标志位中的任何一个,以及TYPE_QUADRANT_ROTATION或TYPE_GENERAL_ROTATION标志位中的任何一个。
